game.description:
Wow! Today you are going to meet with an elephant who loves to sleep. The problem is that he snores so loudly that it can disturb anyone around him. Your job in this brand new arcade challenge is to wake him up. Are you ready to take on this challenge? Join Snoring: Wake Up Elephant and get ready to guide multiple cute animals to wake up Mr. Elephant! This lovely puzzle includes lots of obstacles and plenty of fun and entertainment to enjoy.

You are free to make your animals jump and roll to solve the multiple levels of this animal-themed logical puzzle game for kids and grown-ups. When you click the play button, you would enter the beautiful world of Transilvania where the sleepy elegant and his best friends welcome you wholeheartedly. There are plenty of fun things to watch and enjoy in this friendly atmosphere. This cutest scary-based puzzle features 24 unique and challenging levels to have fun.

The beautiful forest environment coupled with the wonderful graphics, lovely creatures and realistic sound will be sufficient enough to keep you engrossed for hours. Every animal has its own characteristics, so use each one of them according to get the job done and complete all levels. Remember all the other little and cuddly animals fall cannot go to sleep until you the loud of snoring elephant stops. Use the skills of a particular animal to solve different logical puzzles in this mobile phone game!
